727837f-a.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - 69th Street
727837f-a.text:
Queens Boulevard east from 69th Street, showing a contemplated
widening of the Boulevard. View No. 2 shows buildings either
partially in or on the street line. From l-eft (partially seen) to
Nright (dormer windows) are buildings owned or occupied in 1873 by
J. Gebring, J. Frank, Wonrad Stehlirg, and the Nrupp brothers
respectively.
March 1925.
View 2:Fehruary 1924.
Euugene L. Armbruster Collection
